					"type": 23,
					"value": "Piratey AD-song performed by the disguised redcaps in Blushing Mermaid. This song is performed to this https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qP-7GNoDJ5c [Nathan Evans - Wllerman (Sea Shanty)]. These pirates are drunk and roaring out this sea shanty and having a blast (they are secretly redcaps, but they don't transform unless the player attacks them)"
